{"tid":1787389,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府推出紓困措施 3項津貼將於農曆新年前發放","createTime":"2019-12-18T01:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:08:11.000Z","uid":19216,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e9e77ec552199077f9552fb30cd66cb0b6ae12","tid":1787389,"uid":19216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QF4cJ82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQF4cJ82.jpg&h=f7528ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n署理行政長官張建宗早上會見傳媒時表示，政府早前推出的一系列紓緩措施，當中有3項津貼能在明年1月農曆新年前發放，當中包括向綜援、生果金、長者生活津貼和傷殘津貼受惠人發放額外一個月津貼；為較低收入公屋租戶代繳一個月租金；以及2000元電費補貼。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗續說，至於提供幼稚園和中小學學生2500元津貼，以及對中小企的支援措施，亦會在明年首季陸續推出，相信能夠做到「撐企業、保就業、紓民困」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，香港面對前所未有的困難，各界要團結一致，攜手合作、重新起步，強調特區政府會一如以往，嚴正執法，亦會迎難而上，不會因為困難而退縮。"},{"pid":"ca4678b78075051bf3d408c24dbee8bf089111fe","tid":1787389,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎綜援果D 究竟邊忽受到影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb9499e8989aa9bcd659e55238c316a6767b512","tid":1787389,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"綜援、生果金、長者生活津貼和傷殘津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5461a5094af20a815f222c8977e44b9b498bb9","tid":1787389,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca4678b78075051bf3d408c24dbee8bf089111fe","tid":1787389,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎綜援果D 究竟邊忽受到影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"出少左街要補